Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天为大家转播来自永不凋零的樱花树所在小岛的报导
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤井小姐  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我在初音岛为大家带来报导
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----Title-----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:31.47,title,NTP,0,0,0,,Da Capo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寒冷的日子还在继续啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花一直在绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都搞不清楚春天什么时候来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快走就赶不上巴士了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:02:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  学长  葛木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要到毕业典礼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日子过得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到毕业典礼  就是毕业派对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露姐最近也好像忙着做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业派对特刊该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后也从立夏姐那里听说了小樱的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续调查永不凋零的樱花  实在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这件事放一放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的傍晚  究竟会有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}（明天傍晚  来看看永不凋零的樱花树…）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  之前收到的邮件的谜题还没有解开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那条写着“当樱花盛开之时  在约定的那个地方…”的邮件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得应该和这一连串神秘邮件有某种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得只要弄明白昨天收到的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能解开之前收到的邮件的谜题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说一切都会在今天傍晚揭晓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这只是我的感觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定真像清隆说的一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实关于毕业派对特刊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事的话  刚才已经和大家讨论过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:05:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到樱的事  我们觉得应该从别的方向写报导
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得那两人有古怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从小樱那件事之后  该说是距离突然缩短了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于今年的毕业派对  谁有建议…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是干劲十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛  真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请讲  立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏  找回平时的感觉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近都无精打采的  让我很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我想你刚经历过小樱的事  会那样也很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近就那么奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  要说奇怪的话以前就很奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这话是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算啦算啦  不过我们也马上就要毕业了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没剩多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然必须在毕业之前搞清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yahoo  小隆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  露露姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是往常的身体交流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  所以说在学校要自重一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那在家就可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家的哪里可以  起居室？被窝？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说…浴室？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是愿不愿意的问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  姬乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙罗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙罗才是怎么了  找我有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长  放学后还能来看我挥棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挥棒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,垒球部的…不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也想去看你挥棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过今天放学后大家要去邮件中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  今天的沙罗有点奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清隆同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱走了之后  你很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嘛  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  寂寞的时候不用客气  随时跟我说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你想看  裸体围裙随时为你奉上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裸体…围裙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙罗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不纯洁！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.56,MSG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(96,303)\frz23.062}在中庭等你。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才抱歉了  感觉那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说有事…是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那样盯着人家看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心意是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥对谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小隆在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露姐  你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小隆喜欢的是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  夏露露姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只顾着夏露露同学  太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}小隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  大家都在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不纯洁！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耕助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你很累的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是在走廊被夏露露学姐抱住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后也收到沙罗同学挥棒的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还遭到葵同学诱惑  更在中庭和姬乃同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是跟踪狂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你刚才的叹气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“我该选择谁呢  好迷茫啊”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  竟然能为这种事烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好羡慕你这个幸福的奢侈混蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好羡慕你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上没来得及给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在屋顶吃饭  还有点冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许抱怨  这样就暖和了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人看到我们这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清隆会困扰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是接过吻的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  啊…立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏  能问你一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于樱的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…虽然我说不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不知道为什么  我总觉得还能见到樱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏  你知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…关于前世的记忆之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么觉得会和我的前世有关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…立夏你和樱相遇后就恢复了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想是不是和立夏的过去有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且关于樱  你好像也知道一些我不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想听吗  我前世的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该从哪里说起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我可是被称为孤高的洋兰  Category5的魔法使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用魔法解决的事件之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起了许多有趣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想听我和清隆初次结合的那个夜晚的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的清隆十分雄伟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  不是那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事知道了又能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见  芳乃清隆！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们最近好像只顾着一名叫樱的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顾新闻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  用不着你们费心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们忘了吗  我们的胜负还没决出哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没决出哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要真的忘记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负什么的已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧  清隆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  我不允许你们自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到小隆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为你和谁在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了  立夏  一个人独占小隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然之前一直忍着没问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来小隆你的心意究竟在谁身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在问小隆你选谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事确实应该说清楚比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连立夏你也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  这是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你到底选谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  杉并大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们完全被她们放置Play了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部员一号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,败给他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  小隆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要来到这里就没事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续刚才的话题…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在立夏的过去中  樱她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清隆你选谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这件事很重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的不是过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起了什么事情啊  过去是怎样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实在的  这种事怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  只有立夏你一个人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狡猾吗  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就算知道这些事情  未来的发展也不一定一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那样多无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沿着早已知道结局的路线行走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是樱自己所选择的路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是时候做出自己的选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的清隆是如何看待我的  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…这是两回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心意不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我作为现在的我  真的喜欢清隆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  清隆你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说清隆  我们来接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是清隆你自己说的  下次要征求你的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是说过  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  这样就和之前一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次清隆你要主动亲我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  让我们找好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都到齐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  这件事对我们来说是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清隆你选谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像往常一样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说错什么话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  这样算不上回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉白紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种犹豫不决的地方正是清隆的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确有哥哥的风格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好  好久不见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又或者  “初次见面”更好些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  感觉好像不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  刚刚你说“初次见面”…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是  芳乃樱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  另一个我承蒙大家照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“另一个我”？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在别的地方也相遇过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你们的反应  果然没有记忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有…记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所记得的是和你们共同度过的美好时光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及最后一刻所做的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“当樱花盛开之时  在约定的那个地方…”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这封邮件是你发的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然花了些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过又能见到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么  有股很怀念的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是  从刚刚开始就一直这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什么原因  非常的怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我和清隆一起睡的次数是最多的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(170,350)}小隆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(68,350)}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(491,350)}清隆同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(584,350)}不纯洁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清隆还是这么有人气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  你到底知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家能不能听听我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事也许有点长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听完的话  所有的疑问都会得到解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  刚好有点心在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  这是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只能做到这种程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是让人绽放笑容的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就请各位听我道来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个少女和一棵樱花树
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个约定和小小的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及无论经过几十年  几百年都不会改变的  重要的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论四季几度轮回  春天终将到来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带来新鲜的樱花花香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此  宛如Da Capo般循环往复
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18}Da Capo：音乐符号中的返始，指演奏乐章至符号后归回最初并再次重复
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同梦一般的梦境的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起始的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----EDlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:13.02,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}この世界はいつも  移り変わってしまうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:21.03,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここにボクらが存在コトだけは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:21.03,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fs10\pos(130,0)}いる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:27.63,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}変えようのない１つの現実
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:32.19,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}どんな時代を生き抜いても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:43.36,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そこにある笑顔をボクは信じていくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:50.70,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}会いたいよ  会いたいよ  またどこかで…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:56.24,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そう願うのは  ボクのワガママ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:22:01.06,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}会いたいよ  会いたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:09.45,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}またその手であたためて欲しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----EDlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:13.02,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}虽然这个世界总是在改变着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:21.03,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}唯独我们所在的此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:27.63,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}是不容改变的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:32.19,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}无论身处什么时代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:43.36,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你的笑容  都是我的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:50.70,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}好想见你  好想见你  我们何处再会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:56.24,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这份愿望是我的任性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:22:01.06,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}好想见你  好想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:09.45,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}好希望你再次用这双手温暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在问我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.73,0:22:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的胭脂红
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你一样  非常可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这个是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是樱花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  虽然是没见过的品种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱…花

